														secondary metal and precious metal refiners, and supply a variety
														of sow and dross moulds, and other furnace ancillaries.<br>
														<br>
														Ingotech have supplied new and used ingot casting machines to
														users in countries across six continents. We can also refurbish
														machines, of any manufacture, with components to our own high
